{"id":"api/core/TRANSLATIONS","title":"TRANSLATIONS","contents":"\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/TRANSLATIONS\", \"name\": \"TRANSLATIONS\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/i18n/tokens.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L129-L128\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/i18n/tokens.ts#L129-L128\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"translations\">TRANSLATIONS<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TRANSLATIONS#translations\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">當你想用另一種語言翻譯應用程式時，可以在載入程式中使用此令牌來提供翻譯檔案的內容（ <code>xtb</code>、<code>xlf</code> 或 <code>xlf2</code>）</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use this token at bootstrap to provide the content of your translation file (<code>xtb</code>,\n<code>xlf</code> or <code>xlf2</code>) when you want to translate your application in another language.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/core/TRANSLATIONS#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/core/TRANSLATIONS\" class=\"code-anchor\">TRANSLATIONS</a>: <a href=\"api/core/InjectionToken\" class=\"code-anchor\">InjectionToken</a>&lt;string&gt;;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TRANSLATIONS#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">有關更多資訊，請參見<a href=\"guide/i18n#setting-up-locale\">《i18n 指南》</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">See the <a href=\"guide/i18n#merge\">i18n guide</a> for more information.</p>\n\n\n  <p>Further information available in the <a href=\"api/core/TRANSLATIONS#usage-notes\">Usage Notes</a>...</p>\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TRANSLATIONS#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h3 id=\"example\" translation-result=\"on\">例子<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TRANSLATIONS#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TRANSLATIONS#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nimport { <a href=\"api/core/TRANSLATIONS\" class=\"code-anchor\">TRANSLATIONS</a> } from '@angular/core';\nimport { <a href=\"api/platform-browser-dynamic/platformBrowserDynamic\" class=\"code-anchor\">platformBrowserDynamic</a> } from '@angular/platform-browser-dynamic';\nimport { AppModule } from './app/app.module';\n\n// content of your translation file\nconst translations = '....';\n\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser-dynamic/platformBrowserDynamic\" class=\"code-anchor\">platformBrowserDynamic</a>().bootstrapModule(AppModule, {\n  providers: [{provide: <a href=\"api/core/TRANSLATIONS\" class=\"code-anchor\">TRANSLATIONS</a>, useValue: translations }]\n});\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/TRANSLATIONS_FORMAT\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/InjectionToken\n - api/core/TRANSLATIONS#description\n - api/core/TRANSLATIONS#example\n - api/core/TRANSLATIONS#translations\n - api/core/TRANSLATIONS#usage-notes\n - api/platform-browser-dynamic/platformBrowserDynamic\n - guide/i18n#merge\n - guide/i18n#setting-up-locale\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/i18n/tokens.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L129-L128\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/i18n/tokens.ts#L129-L128\n-->"}